in the water.

40
00:01:22,110 --> 00:01:24,430
Anyway, the Chinese destruction of opium

41
00:01:24,430 --> 00:01:26,770
led to the First Opium War.

42
00:01:26,770 --> 00:01:29,850
And the British won Hong Kong Island!

43
00:01:29,850 --> 00:01:31,600
The British had so much fun,

44
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,690
a few years later,

45
00:01:32,690 --> 00:01:35,220
